snippet.title: Swift Fun Algorithms: How to Draw a Circle using Math
snippet.description:
Today's lesson will demonstrate some really good techniques on how to draw lines and circles using the available APIs in Swift.  Because I'm a big fan of incorporating Math into these lessons, I'll walk you through how to apply some sine and cosine equations to establish each point along the arc of our circle.

Enjoy.
